        "created_at": "2017-01-13T11:46:19.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I went back to the importer and the 2012 of this wine is sold out here. I got some of their Clos de Beze (old vines and with some positive reviews). I\u2019ll be looking out for the 2013s when released (even though I know Neal Martin doesn\u2019t rate the wine).</p>",
