        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/i/f05b48/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2017-01-13T14:12:43.000Z",
        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"Howard Davis\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n Howard Davis:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>I went back to the importer and the 2012 of this wine is sold out here. I got some of their Clos de Beze (old vines and with some positive reviews). I\u2019ll be looking out for the 2013s when released (even though I know Neal Martin doesn\u2019t rate the wine).</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Thanks for the note, love these wines. Is Diageo still bringing this in? I thought they were doing away with the imports?</p>\n<p>The Clos de Beze is great, I had some 2000 I bought cheap (like $50), and they were terrific a few years back. I know the 2009 and 2010, but won\u2019t open those for a while.</p>",
